(Hi everyone, Disclaimer: this is a review of a free sample I got sent by Uputronics. I recently) Tj
T*
(spotted on Twitter that Uputronics had launched a GPS/RTS Raspberry Pi Expansion Board, and) Tj
T*
(that they were looking for worthy projects to test it. I thought our Galileo/GPS/BeiDou/GLONASS) Tj
T*
(monitoring project galmon.eu might be worthy and Uputronics agreed. Relevant for our purposes,) Tj
T*
(this is an actual ?timing receiver?. Any GNSS chip will get you a location, but some of them go) Tj
T*
(the extra mile to also deliver a very stable clock signal.) Tj
T*
